.BU
\fCsunos56.gmak\fR Sun Solaris 5.6 using GNU tools
.BU
\fCsunos56.mak\fR Sun Solaris 5.6 native
.BU
\fCsunosx86.gmk\fR Sun Solarais 2.6 (Intel) using GNU tools.
.BU
\fCwin32bc.mak\fR Borland C, 32-bit Windows version.
.BU
\fCwin32b55.mak\fR Borland C 5.5, 32-bit Windows version (Free compiler).
.BU
\fCwin32sv2.mak\fR Microsoft Developer v2.x, Win32s (for Win 3.xx)
.BU
\fCwin32sv4.mak\fR Microsoft Developer v4.2, Win32s (for Win 3.xx)
.BU
